Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:08.98,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord1\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:18.59,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:28.56,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:33.66,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:38.63,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:51.24,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:01:00.94,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:05.78,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:11.45,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:20.75,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:33.25,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:54.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be practicing with only the mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:01:59.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:07.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would love to play tunes like you, Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My way is Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:13.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mess hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:16.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:16.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Craggy, and rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:34.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:51.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:13.88,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}First Battle - Talk of a Chair
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we prepared all this for your arrival last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A sort of welcome meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:37.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring in the fish I was drying upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:41.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least eat breakfast before you sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rio's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The food's going to get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me reintroduce you to the members of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First, our commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Felicia Heidemann, tank commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:32.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel Kannagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporal Kannagi. Pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our mechanic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kureha Suminoya. Gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:17.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:24.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be younger than you, but I have seniority. You'd better listen to everyt-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran out of gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, how about breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:50.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the bacon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:05.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Both soldiers and buglers are all about body strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up and build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When breakfast is over, show her around the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:39.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had work to do, but this was an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm showing you around, under orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:52.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:55.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Insubordination, Private Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Suminoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:04.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First: attention to the national and platoon flags!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank Platoon 1121
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:18.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,currently consists of five members, by rank: one liutenant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:21.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,one sergeant, one corporal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,two privates. Total: five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Private Suminoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be the minimum number for a platoon, but it does mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the few and the proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our platoon has been equipped with the following armaments:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,one heavy machine gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,two light machine guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,four rifles,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:50.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and five handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:58.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our assignment is to defend the national borders of Seize, Trois, with these arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:07:59.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:05.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Suminoya! I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Permission to speak granted, Private Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If my memory serves me, then next to Seize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, beyond the mountains is Nomansland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:27.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the borders of Helvetia only extend to this region, so this is the national border!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:28.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The front lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A strategic position!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not allow a pre-emptive strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We trade off watch duty through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping is strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:43.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the only hotline connecting to the capital in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rings, something big is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, everyone is to be woken up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and immediately placed on full alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Private Suminoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,On the second floor are the commander's quarters and the operations room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance is strictly-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But make sure you knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the latrines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Readying the bath and cleaning are done in turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathing order is by rank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:46.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's more fun if everyone bathes together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:48.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But today is Noel's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But she looks tired today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, if you're like that, the recruit will never learn discipline!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:05.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it later, so be commander-like and stay firm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:28.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:32.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the tank deployed for Platoon 1121's use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:36.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Zero Series Autonomous Walker Tank, the Takemikadzuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so much bigger than the ones at training!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of those zero-generation tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:49.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are less than ten still in operation in the country. A treasure from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to be really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But its legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's undergoing repairs, but we don't have enough parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:08.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have the servicing manual and we can't find any parts for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:12.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but Noel is doing something about it, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This tank... I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:33.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, our unit is completely lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:37.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They even call us Seize's extra baggage or a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:41.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got pink epaulettes but we don't even have an operational tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:47.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:52.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're already getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:57.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us when we had just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:07.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After you sent Kanata to sleep last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, why did we get communications personnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:15.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the new recruit would be a loader or a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters sent her to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:23.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't always get what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:23.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there now. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:31.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio will take care of you the way she always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like she always has.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's young, but she has good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She might already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:57.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:05.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:10.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:24.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were seeing things half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:25.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you thought so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the ghost, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the barracks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going along with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's normal for ghosts to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you stop playing along with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Noel, I'm disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:49.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an engineer! You're supposed to investigate this scientifically before reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no such things as ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No such things, no such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No possible way there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with you completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. There are no such things as ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance of a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspect the area thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the event you encounter the enemy, blow your bugle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll send you reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kana- Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunder is like a marching beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:52.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Kana-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami! You go in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:57.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:58.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:17.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This part was left the way it was before it was turned into a fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:24.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would know? Just hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideographs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:57.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't read it, there's no point staring at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be wonderful if I could read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just nonsense from a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How can't you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:20.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But ghosts are things that protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:27.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the village I was born, we had a festival every year to thank the ghosts that protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of village would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:37.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Ghosts possess people, drink blood, move corpses, and are just pure evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:57.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes rats can carry diseases-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Well, aren't you sca-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this was a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:41.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There probably isn't a school this big, even in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:45.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there used to be a lot more people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:51.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm sure that this building was filled with kids about our age,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and they would study together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have taught music here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't read the words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D-sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:21.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Notes never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:44.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:58.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Seize, this fortress, everyone in our platoon. All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:06.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a tiny little unit in the middle of nowhere that doesn't even matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our tank is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And they forget to send us supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just soldiers in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:29.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:43.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:04.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wonderful, ever so wonderful, Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is our ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the "ghost" part?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like that thief from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You...You're dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't frighten her when she's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably just doesn't have a place to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And what was our unit's symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Making roasted owl is like roasting ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it, Shuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave it a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:00.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you nearly died yesterday because of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:03.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got to have an amazing adventure because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the furthest thing from an adventure there could be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:16.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. Maybe we should be democratic about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:17.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:23.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she steals food again, then she'll be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you played this morning, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:14.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The townspeople would complain if we let Kanata play it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:16.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:24.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:31.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:36.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to find another one of these chairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:39.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it for you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:40.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:44.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:49.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:51.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:57.98,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.45,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:19.21,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:25.30,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:34.08,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:38.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.31,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:44.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you tell me who you're asking to the dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:45.86,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:51.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.29,0:23:51.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, we'll be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:57.67,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:57.67,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you count my precious hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:03.67,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All the usual words can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.93,0:24:09.51,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.83,0:24:14.46,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:26.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: A Day in the Life - Rio Runs
